f more than 250,000 locations and has completed projects for companies such as Comcast, Disney, the FBI, Facebook, Google, and many more.<\/p>","text_color":"#000000","button_text_color":"#000000","button_text_color_hover":"#ffffff","mobile_heading_font_size":"text-xl","desktop_heading_font_size":"md:text-xl","mobile_content_font_size":"text-base","desktop_content_font_size":"md:text-base","copy_bottom_spacing":16,"desktop_col_span":"md:w-1\/2","column_text_alignment":"text-left"}},"de25ebff-2f99-48c0-ad53-89bb4a851ceb":{"type":"multicolumn-text","settings":{"heading":"<p>Business Situation<\/p>","copy":"<p>When a customer needed the ability to angle a long range card reader, Pedestal PRO came to RAM® Mounts. While a competitor in their space had a solution, it didn’t cover wires and lacked a clean look. With an initial concept in mind, the experts at Pedestal PRO knew there had to be a better way – specifically with the experience and engineering prowess offered by RAM®.<\/p>","text_color":"#000000","button_text_color":"#000000","button_text_color_hover":"#ffffff","mobile_heading_font_size":"text-xl","desktop_heading_font_size":"md:text-xl","mobile_content_font_size":"text-base","desktop_content_font_size":"md:text-base","copy_bottom_spacing":16,"desktop_col_span":"md:w-1\/2","column_text_alignment":"text-left"}},"8635440c-c09c-4e14-94e1-be9db94136fa":{"type":"multicolumn-text","settings":{"heading":"<p>Our Solution<\/p>","copy":"<p>It didn’t take long for a solution to take shape after Pedestal PRO approached RAM® Mounts with the issue and a concept. After initial discussions, no other company was even considered for the job. The custom solution completely covers the wires as they pass through the mount to the attached card reader, and can be positioned on the pedestal in whatever way is needed.<\/p>","text_color":"#000000","button_text_color":"#000000","button_text_color_hover":"#ffffff","mobile_heading_font_size":"text-xl","desktop_heading_font_size":"md:text-xl